          "content": [
            {
              "text": "Use \"sign in\" to describe using a username and password in starting a session on VantageCloud Lake or other Teradata products. Use \"sign out\" to refer to ending a session.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "attrs": {
            "textAlign": "left"
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "Don't use \"log in,\" \"login,\" \"log into,\" \"log on,\" \"logon,\" \"log onto,\" \"log off,\" \"log out,\" \"logout,\" \"signin,\" \"sign-in,\"Â \"sign into,\" \"sign-off,\" \"sign off,\" \"sign on,\" or \"sign-on\"",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "italic"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "text": "(with the exception of \"single sign-on\").",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "attrs": {
            "textAlign": "left"
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "Avoid using the noun or adjective form such as \"sign-in\" or \"signed-out.\" Instead, use the verb form because it gives the most clarity.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  },
